{"tid":2211343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲記唔記得當初嗰團火?","createTime":"2020-09-21T05:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T11:48:42.000Z","uid":371519,"like":25,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"7b74b958c2b1627d44b59291d3d6bd7b2fb40dc2","tid":2211343,"uid":371519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:21:31.000Z","msg":"呢埸運動嘅初衷係咩仲記唔記得？<br />\n仲記唔記得呢條片入面嘅場景？當初嗰種憤怒仲喺度嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/imjZ7aHZRuY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FimjZ7aHZRuY&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZovsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=bc1dba3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/imjZ7aHZRuY</a><br />\n<br />\n好多人話場運動靜咗，<span class=\"red\">其實靜咗嗰個係你自己</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想重蹈覆轍，行雨傘舊路可以點做?<br />\n<br />\n<ins>1. 做文宣</ins><br />\n見唔到集中嘅文宣就以為冇？其實仲有好多人做緊!!! 巴士 貼紙 post ig咩都得，只要你肯做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>2. Twitter Reddit</ins><br />\nRepost+like基本野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾多啲外國人知香港發生緊咩事，就算受眾唔多都好過冇做<br />\n<br />\n<ins>3. 旁聽/寫信</ins><br />\n支持被捕手足，比佢哋知道仍有人關心佢哋，比佢哋知道佢並唔係一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>4. 保持憤怒，唔好遺忘初衷</ins><br />\n成日話香港人善忘，你睇吓熱門就知<br />\n唔好俾自己忘記嗰種憤怒同抗爭熱度，先有動力繼續行落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>5. 唔好成日掛住屌自己人</ins><br />\n我哋嘅敵人唔係自己友，成日圍內鬥黃好玩咩? <br />\n有時間屌自己人不如做Twitter task做文宣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家可唔可以團結啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>6. 唔好懶</ins><br />\n有用嘅要做，冇乜用嘅都要做，做咗點都好過冇做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n疫情下其實仲有好多嘢可以做，最緊要唔好俾自己靜落嚟<br />\n一日未光復香港，一日都唔好放棄<br />\n要保持一個肯思考嘅腦，唔好比政府PR搞亂我哋自己，千祈唔好行返舊路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adfb02efd86163fc1f354dad98c8645e6bef263","tid":2211343,"uid":371519,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:21:57.000Z","msg":"第一次開post，屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5ef902887feb80c7ee8d158c3bd2a334207e06","tid":2211343,"uid":78703,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:23:01.000Z","msg":"時事台巴打：唔街頭抗爭，根本keep唔到團火"},{"pid":"2858f77f8ef477f827ef9f22ed9f874788ce4105","tid":2211343,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:23:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c220dfdf2c6877b0cab8e36efc4c8012318e56ae","tid":2211343,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:24:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52ac7429b46dce1dd70cec17011f2ab8e81a544c","tid":2211343,"uid":100016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:24:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d50cef3059c40703b9420bb7b85b617dfd035f67","tid":2211343,"uid":371519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ed5ef902887feb80c7ee8d158c3bd2a334207e06","tid":2211343,"uid":78703,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:23:01.000Z","msg":"時事台巴打：唔街頭抗爭，根本keep唔到團火"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:24:56.000Z","msg":"事在人為嘅啫<br />\n街頭抗爭只係抗爭嘅其中一種形式，仲有好多種方法可以做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ff249629ec1c505d67384e17e1085f1e16e112","tid":2211343,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:26:09.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9411c9df4a47e6341d928f726acf0650578fa58","tid":2211343,"uid":371519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"52ac7429b46dce1dd70cec17011f2ab8e81a544c","tid":2211343,"uid":100016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:24:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:27:56.000Z","msg":"好多人覺得靜咗，係因為冇再咁關心件事<br />\n呢